methods.manage:
Add the specified referent to this manager. referent must be live. If this manager is also a
 LivenessReferent, then it must also be live.

:param referent: (io.deephaven.engine.liveness.LivenessReferent) - The referent to add
methods.tryManage:
Attempt to add referent to this manager. Will succeed if referent is live and if this manager is
 not a LivenessReferent or is live.

:param referent: (io.deephaven.engine.liveness.LivenessReferent) - The referent to add
:return: (boolean) Whether the referent was in fact added

text: Interface for objects that retainReference LivenessReferents until such time as they are no longer necessary.
